arcade.core.agent.cell

Interface Cell

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PatchCell, PatchCellCancer, PatchCellCancerStem, PatchCellTissue, PottsCell

    public interface Cell
extends sim.engine.Steppable
    A Cell object represents a cell agent.

    Each cell is associated with a Location object that defines their physical location. Each cell is also associated with a Module object and/or Process objects that characterizes cellular behaviors and states. The Module or Process object(s) are stepped during the step method of the Cell.
